WHEREAS, his career embodies the very qualities for which the Bob Easterly
Award was established, including leadership, service, lifelong commitment to professional
excellence, and the economic well being of Livingston Parish.
THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Senate of the Legislature of Louisiana
does hereby commend and congratulate Fernand "Ferdie" P. Genre upon receiving the
Livingston Economic Development Council's Bob Easterly Award.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to
Fernand "Ferdie" P. Genre.
PRESIDENT OF THE SENATE
